DeferredValueSwap — AI-Powered Intelligent Escrow on GenLayer
Overview

This system implements an intelligent escrow protocol for GenLayer, enabling two parties to execute trustless agreements such as freelance work, product sales, or service delivery.

A sender locks GEN as collateral. A recipient either:

receives a payout (financial settlement), or
receives a certificate (NFT-like proof of completion)

If a dispute occurs, resolution can be:

manual (contract owner)
AI-driven (LLM-based arbitration using full deal context)

This creates a hybrid execution model combining deterministic smart contract logic with AI-assisted decision-making.

